+!!! note
+    When using the `ktlint_official` code style, no wildcard imports are allowed by default. In other code styles, wildcard imports from `java.util.*` and `kotlinx.android.synthetic.**` are allowed by default to keep in sync with IntelliJ IDEA behavior.
